column1: ## (3) regulatorGeneName. Gene(s) coding for the TF
## (4) regulatedId. Transcription Unit ID regulated by the TF (regulated Transcription Unit)
## (5) regulatedName. Transcription Unit regulated by the TF (regulated Transcription Unit)
## (6) function. Regulatory Function of the TF on the regulated Transcription Unit (+ activator, - repressor, +- dual, ? unknown)
## (7) confidenceLevel. RI confidence level based on its evidence (Values: Confirmed[C], Strong[S], Weak[W], Unknown[?])
